  <Notes>
    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>06100202100027</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>In {S:06100202100026} ἀνακάμπτω occurs in an apparatus variant in a figurative sense of returning to a previous state with regard to divine revelation.</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References>
        <Reference>06100202100027</Reference>
      </References>
      <Content>The substitution of ἀνακάμπτω for ὑποστρέφω in certain manuscripts of {S:06100202100026} would indicate clearly how closely these terms seem to be related in meaning. Any distinctions of meaning which they may have had would evidently be connotative.</Content>
    </Note>
